Title: Justice League
Writer: Chris Terrio (screenplay), Zack Snyder (story by), Chris Terrio (story by), Bob Kane (characters), Bill Finger (characters), William Moulton Marston (character created by: Wonder Woman), Joe Shuster (characters), Jerry Siegel (characters)
Actors: Gal Gadot, Amber Heard, Jason Momoa, Diane Lane
Plot: Fueled by his restored faith in humanity and inspired by Superman's selfless act, Bruce Wayne enlists the help of his newfound ally, Diana Prince, to face an even greater enemy.
